v5.16.0: Rebalance scoring, merge categories, streamline navigation

Scoring weights: 40/30/30 to 35% Science / 25% Community / 40% Commonness
across both quiz recommendation engine and Top Strains curated lists.

Quiz effects:
- Merged Calm and Ease (anxiety_relief) into Relaxation
- Added Appetite as a selectable quiz goal (CB1 + ghrelin pathways)

Top Strains categories:
- Combined Energy and Focus into single category (10 from 11)
- Regenerated all lists with new 35/25/40 weights

Navigation:
- Removed Dashboard (low-value hub, all features in dedicated pages)
- Combined Taste Profile into Journal page as Profile tab
- Desktop nav: 9 items to 7 (Quiz, Search, Explorer, Top For, Journal, Compare, Learn)
- /dashboard and /preferences redirect to /journal
